Wendy Allnutt https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wendy_Allnutt 0 Wendy Allnutt (born 1 May 1946) is an English stage and screen actress. She now teaches at the Guildhall School of Music and Drama, leading a degree course in Training Actors Movement. Wendy_Allnutt ( born 1_May_1946 ) is an_English_stage_and_screen_actress .
